  <summary>5/19/1999--Introduced.
Public Hearing Standardization Act of 1999 - Directs the Secretary of the Interior to establish by regulation general requirements for conducting public hearings on certain agency actions. Requires such regulations to be designed to help ensure that the public understands and can fully participate in public hearings.</summary>
